Package: iSCORE.PDecipher
Title: Integrated Analysis of Parkinson's Disease Mutations and Perturbations
Version: 0.1.2
Authors@R: 
    person("Jesse", "Dunnack", , "jesse.dunnack@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = ""))
Description: iSCORE-PDecipher provides integrated analysis tools for Parkinson's disease
    research, combining iSCORE-PD mutation data with PerturbSeq (CRISPRi/CRISPRa) experiments.
    It includes differential expression analysis using MAST and MixScale, comprehensive
    functional enrichment analysis, and interactive Shiny visualization tools.
